\">IA High Tec Shop</div>\n      <div class=\"item-name\">Smart Watch 2.0</div>\n      <div class=\"item-variant\" id=\"itemVariant\">Couleur : Noir</div>\n      <div class=\"item-badge\">−50% • Offre Live</div>\n      <div class=\"item-bottom\">\n        <div class=\"item-price-wrap\">\n          <div class=\"item-price\" id=\"itemPrice\">64,90 €</div>\n          <div class=\"item-price-old\">129,90 €</div>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-end;gap:6px;\">\n          <div class=\"item-qty\">\n            <button class=\"qty-btn\" onclick=\"changeQty(-1)\">−</button>\n            <span class=\"qty-val\" id=\"itemQty\">1</span>\n            <button class=\"qty-btn\" onclick=\"changeQty(1)\">+</button>\n          </div>\n          <button class=\"item-remove\" onclick=\"removeItem()\">Retirer</button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"upsell-block\" id=\"upsellBlock\">\n  <div class=\"upsell-title\">Souvent ajouté ensemble</div>\n  <div class=\"upsell-item\">\n    <div class=\"upsell-img\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0850/9571/0986/files/hf_20260405_142202_2505abc6-1f9d-4225-8941-b8cd2f3aff86.png?v=1775399077\" alt=\"Bracelet supplémentaire\">\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"upsell-info\">\n      <div class=\"upsell-name\">Bracelet Sport Premium</div>\n      <div class=\"upsell-price\">+9,90 €</div>\n    </div>\n    <button class=\"upsell-add\" id=\"upsellBtn\" onclick=\"addUpsell()\">+ Ajouter</button>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"summary-block\" id=\"summary-block\">\n  <div class=\"summary-title\">Récapitulatif</div>\n  <div class=\"summary-row\"><span class=\"summary-label\">Sous-total</span><span class=\"summary-val\" id=\"subtotal\">64,90 €</span></div>\n  <div class=\"summary-row saving\"><span class=\"summary-label\">🎉 Économie réalisée</span><span class=\"summary-val\" id=\"savingVal\">−65,00 €</span></div>\n  <div class=\"summary-row\